Coaches, take your team’s training to the next level by booking your practices at
Coastal Elite Sports’ premier indoor batting cages
! Rain or shine, our climate-controlled facility provides the perfect environment for focused, uninterrupted work on hitting mechanics, timing, and technique. With top-quality equipment, multiple lanes, and flexible scheduling, our cages are ideal for individual or team sessions. Whether you're in preseason prep or mid-season tune-ups, give your players the edge with professional-level training space — all conveniently located right here in Walton County.

Indoor Batting Cages Facility in Freeport, FL
Experience Freeport’s best Indoor batting cage facility!
At Coastal Elite Sports, we offer Northwest Florida’s finest indoor batting cages, designed to enhance the training and performance of both baseball and softball players. Located in the heart of Freeport, our newly equipped facility includes five full-length pitching and batting cages equipped with professional-grade surfaces and equipment, ensuring a premier experience for athletes at all skill levels.
Perfect for All Ages and Skill Levels
Our batting cages are ideal for players of all ages and skill levels. Whether you're a young athlete just starting out or a seasoned player looking to refine your skills, Coastal Elite Sports provides a welcoming environment that supports growth and development. Our facility is designed to cater to both casual hitters and serious competitors, offering a versatile space for training and practice.
Expert Instruction and Private Lessons
At Coastal Elite Sports, we understand the importance of personalized coaching. Our experienced instructors offer expert guidance through private lessons and group clinics, tailored to meet the needs of each individual athlete. With a focus on improving techniques and strategies, our coaches are dedicated to helping players reach their full potent
Join Our Community
We invite you to become a part of the Coastal Elite Sports community. Our facility is not just about practice; it’s about building a supportive network of athletes and families who share a passion for sports. Participate in our leagues, tournaments, events, camps, and clinics to find your unique love for the game and develop your skills in a dynamic and engaging environment.
Indoor Pickleball
Our facility features two indoor ATP ready pickleball courts complete with championship nets, perfect for players of all ages and skill levels.
Learn More
Batting Cages
Five full length batting cages, equipped for both baseball & softball hitting, pitching & fielding training.
Learn More
Golf Simulators
Our PGA Recognized Indoor Golf studio features TruGolf Simulators for both practice & play.
Learn More
Private Instruction
Looking for private lessons? Our experienced coaches offer personalized training for all skill levels.
Learn More
